Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.77,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fn汉仪颜楷W\b0\3aFF\bord1\blur2\shad2\fs120\1c6AEFFF\4c856D1D\pos(689,440)}閃避球
